Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,基本上都收拾掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,莉雅絲小姐她們沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,回家吧 愛西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我們還要一起參加運動會的二人三腳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,得去練習…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不能饒恕 不能饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,砍 我要砍死你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,潔諾薇亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,把愛西亞還我 她是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,很溫柔 她比任何人還要溫柔…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,社長 愛西亞不見了 得快點去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我的…是我們重要的家人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 吉蒙里的公主真是惡趣味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊的紅色骯髒東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.59,0:04:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經把那丫頭丟到次元的另一頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,她應該已經屍骨無存了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說她死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 法夫納 陪我鬧一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,瑟傑克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你這個可恨的虛偽的存在！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,克魯澤雷 為了讓惡魔這個種族繼續存活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,現在的冥界不需要戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你這不單跟墮天使 甚至還跟天使勾結的混蛋 沒資格談論惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.66,0:05:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你加入了禍之團這種被排斥者的俱樂部還真能說出這種話來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,克魯澤雷 我作為魔王 我現在要排除與冥界敵對的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這、這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真貨要輸給假貨…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我把他連同在他體內蠢蠢欲動的蛇一併消滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到你自己會出場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,阿撒塞勒 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,莉雅絲•吉蒙里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,赤龍帝…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不想死就馬上離開這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊的惡魔 你叫夏爾巴來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你搞錯了選項
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這個靈氣的量和力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,到底發生了什麼事？一誠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}吾，乃覺醒者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}乃自神奪得霸之理之二天龍也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,對呢 一直都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}嗤笑無限 憂慮夢幻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,世界所尋求的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,世界所否定的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}吾 當成赤龍之霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都是力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都是愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不論多少次都會選擇將你毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}將汝沉入紅蓮煉獄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}「霸龍」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs30}Juggernaut Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,將你就地解決的話 世界就能得到和平嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能 吾乃不敗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.93,0:08:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你明明擁有如此強大的力量 但是卻對這世界毫無興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可你如今又是為何會成為恐怖分子首領的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,靜寂的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,想回到作為故鄉的次元狹縫 獲得寂靜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.26,0:08:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,想回到次元狹縫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我記得那個好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣 瓦力 你的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我說瓦力 它真的在這種次元狹縫裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,總有一天會找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,兵藤一誠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,變更計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我們現在去冥界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,突然間怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,愛西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,別開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好好品嘗我的制裁之光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Divid
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Divid Divid Divid Divid Divid Divid Divid…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,居然是白龍皇的光翼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(703,650)}Divine Dividing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那股力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠之前奪走的瓦利的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦利 無論在哪你都要妨礙我嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡的怪物 這就是所謂的「霸龍」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,加斯帕的停止能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就連我的力量也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Boost Boost Boost Boost Boost Boost Boost Boost Boost…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕 這樣下去連我們也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,社長 我們暫時撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,莉雅絲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,社長 失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,…Boost Boost Boost Boost Boost Boost
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,「朗基努斯擊碎者」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,650)}Longinus Smasher
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 紅龍 白龍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,難道我們只能袖手旁觀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠學長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.84,0:11:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,該怎麼做 我們該怎麼做才能讓一誠恢復原狀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.66,0:11:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是「霸龍」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,白龍皇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是察覺的兵藤一誠的異變 所以過來看看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.67,0:11:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那是兵藤一誠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,看來變成了「半吊子」的霸龍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,能恢復原狀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因為是不完全狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:12:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,有能夠變回去的情況 也有就這樣繼續削減生命至死為止的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他那樣肯定有生命危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,愛西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:07.30,BackGround,,0,0,0,,愛西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我們在次元狹縫中移動的時候偶然發現了這名少女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,運氣真是棒呢 要是沒被我們發現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,這位姐姐就會被次元狹縫的無所侵蝕 而消失了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,莉雅絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,只要將愛西亞平安無事的結果告訴他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠應該就能解除那種狀態了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,靠近他就會喪命的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 我是不會阻止你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.26,0:12:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我一個人去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,社長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:37.40,BackGround,,0,0,0,,莉雅絲社長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠就由我救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你了 請你救救一誠學長和莉雅絲社長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是擁有白皇龍之力的你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.03,0:12:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,白龍皇禁手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,650)}Vanishing Dragon Balance Breaker
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算做什麼 瓦力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是去壓制他的力量而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,以他現在是那種狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,白龍皇的光翼必須要觸碰到對方的身體才能發揮效用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(287,650)}Divine Dividing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他現在是那種狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 所以需要以眼還眼 以龍還龍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}吾 乃覺醒者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}乃遭霸之理奪取一切之二天龍也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}嫉妒無限，思念夢幻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}吾 當極白龍之霸道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.01,0:13:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}邀汝進入無垢極限！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}「霸龍」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\i1}Juggernaut Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,兵藤一誠 你是我的競爭對手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Divid
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Divid
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Divid
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Divid
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下就看你們的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.76,0:14:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠 快變回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.72,0:14:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字是愛西亞•阿基多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,請叫我愛西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:14:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,愛西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可以交到很多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,跟朋友一起去買花束和書籍 一起聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,愛西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,即使為時不長 但是我還是交到朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的感到非常幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不過她已經死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.66,0:15:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那個孩子也死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,戲弄不懂女生的男生真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我擺出很困擾的表情 你馬上就會關心我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是那都是我故意演的戲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以去死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠 你不記得我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有點奇怪 他的波動與純粹的龍略有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,中間混雜著別的什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你來了啊 奧菲斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 看著我 一誠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你為我流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有保護好你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,又一次沒能保護好你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 你沒保護好她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那時如此 現在也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,住手！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,社長…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠 要是你不在了的話 我也沒有活下去的意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.25,0:17:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你無法回來的話 我和你一起消失也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…一誠…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所以！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,社長…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,莉雅絲…社長…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你回來了 你回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠 我的一誠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那中間混雜的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠學長×2
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,社長…你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.54,0:18:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,愛西亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是被瓦利他們救下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,只是偶然而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,愛西亞 愛西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？一誠先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.35,0:18:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,愛西亞 太好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,愛西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:39.22,BackGround,,0,0,0,,愛西亞 愛西亞 愛西亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,潔諾薇亞同學 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,愛西亞 我們是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,永遠永遠都是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 不要再丟下我一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 永遠都是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,愛西亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:18:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,兵藤一誠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好好看著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是我想看到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,龍中之龍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,650)}Dragon of Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,人稱DxD 真赤龍神帝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,偉大之紅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,650)}Great Red
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,偉大之紅…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,DxD…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.11,0:19:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,自願棲息在次元夾縫 永遠飛翔於其中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那既是奧菲斯的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.32,0:19:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,也是我想打倒的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,目標？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.93,0:19:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要成為真白龍皇——白龍神皇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,總有一天我要打倒這個偉大之紅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,偉大之紅<Great Red> 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才還不在這的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:20:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,奧菲斯 無限龍神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.20,0:20:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(707,650)}Uroboros Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,奧菲斯就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,禍之團的老大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,吾終有一天將獲得靜寂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,兵藤一誠 你想打倒我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.34,0:20:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 當然想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,要是社長還有朱乃姐的歐派縮小一半的話可是要出大事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你果然很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,變得更強大吧 兵藤一誠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 回家吧 回我們的家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,社長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.40,0:20:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了偉大之紅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,只是看到他的樣子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,只有這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,還有各種其他原因嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,卡特蕾雅 克魯澤雷 夏爾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,既然是崇高的前魔王的血族後裔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那就要為這種生存的方式而驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,話說 你幫赤龍帝的理由是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真不像你的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一時興起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可能一切都還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,給我記住了 兵藤一誠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.67,0:21:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,社長 我好像又亂來 讓你傷腦筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.05,0:21:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有 你是最棒的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.59,0:21:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你是我最棒的僕人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.70,0:21:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我永遠都是社長的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,對你而言 和平也是會伴隨著痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.34,0:21:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一誠！！！
